<html>
  <head>
    <title>Trademarkers Notification | IMPORTANT!! Please read carefully</title>
  <style>
    body, p{
      font-size: 11.0pt;
      font-family: Consolas;
      line-height: 14pt;
    }
    p{
      margin:0;
    }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body>
<p style="margin:0">
  <% 
  let name = mailData.user.name.split(',')
  %>
  Dear <%= name[1] ? name[1].trim() : 'Trademarkers Client' %>,
</p>

<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0">
  Today I have good news for you: The United States Patent and Trademark Office (USPTO) has issued a “Notice of Allowance” (NOA), which means that in principle you have received the green light for your brand <%= mailData.trademark.name %> to be registered as a trademark.
</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0">
  Now unlike many other trademark jurisdictions, the USPTO makes the registration of a trademark dependent on actual use, and such use has to be declared and proven by filing what is called a “Statement of Use”.
</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0">
  Alongside with your declaration, you need to include a “specimen” (like a photo, screen grab of a website where the product is offered etc.) – as the examiner needs to see that you are actually offering the product or service to the public in the United States.
</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0">
  You have 6 months from the issue date of the NOA (which was on <%= mailData.dateFiledFormatted %>) to file such a statement. If you are not using the trademark now and you are unable to declare use within that time frame, you can file for an extension and get another 6 months (but there are limits after that).
</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0">
  At this point, you have several options – please click on the following link, which is self-explanatory:<br> 
<a href="https://www.trademarkers.com/<%= mailData.number %>/statement-of-use" target="_blank" >
  https://www.trademarkers.com/<%= mailData.number %>/statement-of-use
</a>
</p>

<% if ( mailData.showUsptoLink ) { %>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0">
  You can see this "Notice of Allowance" (and the continued progress of your trademark application) in the database of the USPTO at: <br>
  <a href="https://tsdr.uspto.gov/documentviewer?caseId=<%= mailData.serialNumber %>" target="_blank" >
    https://tsdr.uspto.gov/documentviewer?caseId=<%= mailData.serialNumber %>
  </a>
</p>
<% } %>

<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0">
  If you have any more questions, let me know!
</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p >Best regards,
</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p >Michael</p>
<p >Customer Service Specialist</p>
<p style="margin:0">&nbsp;</p>
<p style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";margin:0;font-weight:800'>TRADEMARKERS LLC</p>
<p style="margin:0"><i><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Tahoma","sans-serif";margin:0;'><a href="http://www.trademarkers.com" target="_blank">www.trademarkers.com</a></span></i></p>

</body>
</html>